oads/2023/07/Untitled-12.jpg"></a></p><p>招聘期限：未定</p><p>VTuber/虚拟肝脏组合“ <a href="https://www.vase.tokyo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VASE”</a>正在举办VTuber独家招募选拔赛。</p><p>目前，正在海选的“女歌手偶像VTuber”、“男歌手偶像VTuber”、“女游戏偶像VTuber”、“男游戏偶像VTuber”、“女松户市本土偶像VTuber”、“女地区本土偶像VTuber”我们正在招聘。</p><p> <a href="https://artstone-entertainment.movabletype.io/audition.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击此处</a>获取申请表。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000016.000038426.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">艺石娱乐有限公司新闻稿</a></p><h2 id="link14">青桐高中永久试镜</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/Untitled-13.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/Untitled-13.jpg"></a></p><p>招聘期限：永久</p><p>VTuber团体“<a href="https://aogirihighschool.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">青桐高中</a>”正在举办永久VTuber试镜。</p><p>申请人必须有YouTube、Nico Nico直播、SHOWROOM等平台的投放经验，能够连续直播至少一年，并且能够每周至少直播四次。</p><p><a href="http://aogiri-hs.com/audition.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>查看特别试镜页面。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000056.000044525.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">勇敢团体新闻稿</a></p><h2 id="link15">《Holo Live》独家VTuber试镜</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/Untitled-46.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/Untitled-46-1024x674.png"></a></p><p>招聘期限：永久</p><p>VTuber办公室“ <a href="https://www.hololive.tv/bosyu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Holo Live Production</a> ”随时举办VTuber试镜。连续投放1年以上是可以的，条件是每周可以投放3次以上。我们还在寻找有提供游戏、歌曲、插图等记录的人。</p><p> <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScMqA2waFXgE868VpM8keCdWaKjlOWsD3TgD2hsSqev6bE-Zw/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>查看特别试镜页面。</p><h2 id="link16"> 《Holostars》独家VTuber试镜</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/Untitled-47.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023